OL,3,CWhat does the UK's social media ban
OL,4,Cmean for the Channel Islands?
OL,6,FCritics say that the Channel Islands
OL,7,Fhave "fallen behind" on online safety
OL,8,Fafter UK Prime Minister, Sir Keir
OL,9,FStarmer, announced plans to ban social
OL,10,Fmedia for under-16s.
OL,12,FJersey Deputy-elect Catherine Curtis
OL,13,Ftold ITV News that "children in Jersey
OL,14,Fdon't have much protection at all".
OL,16,FShe highlighted the island's lack of
OL,17,Fonline age verification and "network-
OL,18,Flevel filtering" of its telecoms
OL,19,Fnetwork.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
