OL,3,CWhat does the UK's social media ban
OL,4,Cmean for the Channel Islands?
OL,6,FJersey chose not to automatically
OL,7,Fadopt the UK's Online Safety Act,
OL,8,Fwhich came into force last year.
OL,10,FThat law has strengthened safeguards
OL,11,Fto prevent young people from accessing
OL,12,Finappropriate and extreme content,
OL,13,Fwhile introducing punishments for
OL,14,Flarge technology companies that run
OL,15,Fsocial media platforms.
OL,17,FOn Monday, the UK Prime Minister went
OL,18,Ffurther, stating that his Government
OL,19,Fwill block children under the age of
OL,20,F16 from going on a range of popular
OL,21,Fsocial media and live streaming sites.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
