OL,3,CWhat does the UK's social media ban
OL,4,Cmean for the Channel Islands?
OL,6,FThe ban would include Snapchat,
OL,7,FInstagram, Facebook, TikTok, X and
OL,8,FYouTube, but not WhatsApp.
OL,10,FThe UK's announcement follows
OL,11,Fcountries such as Australia and
OL,12,FDenmark, which have already passed
OL,13,Flegislation to restrict access to
OL,14,Fcertain platforms based on age.
OL,16,FOliver McCreedy, 17, is a Jersey
OL,17,Fstudent and says he supports the ban,
OL,18,Fadding that social media distracted
OL,19,Fhim during his GCSEs.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
