OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1781808494
OL,3,CWhat does the UK's social media ban
OL,4,Cmean for the Channel Islands?
OL,6,FHe explains: "I think it's really good
OL,7,Fto focus on school work but also other
OL,8,Fhobbies."
OL,10,FThe President of Guernsey's Education,
OL,11,FSport and Culture Committee, Deputy
OL,12,FPaul Montague, says Guernsey will
OL,13,F"watch what the UK can do" but that
OL,14,Fthe States would be "cautious" on
OL,15,Fbringing in its own changes.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
