CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1781808494
OL,3,CWhat does the UK's social media ban
OL,4,Cmean for the Channel Islands?
OL,6,FSome critics of the ban have raised
OL,7,Fconcerns that restricting access to
OL,8,Fsocial media would disproportionally
OL,9,Faffect marginalised teenagers and
OL,10,Fthose who use it as a safe space,
OL,11,Fpushing them further into unregulated
OL,12,Fareas of the Internet.
OL,14,FIt is not clear yet how the UK's
OL,15,Fannouncement will affect the Channel
OL,16,FIslands. Whilst Jersey and Guernsey
OL,17,Fset their own laws, the social media
OL,18,Fgiants may not differentiate and could
OL,19,Fapply blanket restrictions across the
OL,20,FBritish Isles.
